flowchart TD
    %% Standard UML Activity Diagram Start and End nodes
    Start((Start))
    Finish(((End)))

    Start --> Login[Authenticate User]
    Login --> Dashboard[View Dashboard]

    Dashboard --> CheckSetup{Topic Exists?}
    
    %% Setup Branch
    CheckSetup -->|No| CreateTopic[Create Subject and Topic]
    CreateTopic --> Upload[Upload PDF Material]
    
    CheckSetup -->|Yes| Upload

    %% Parallel Processing Path
    Upload --> Async[Background: Process PDF and Generate Vectors]
    Upload --> TakeQuiz[Select Topic to Start Quiz]

    %% Quiz Loop
    TakeQuiz --> FetchQ[Retrieve Pre-generated Questions]
    FetchQ --> Answer[Submit Answer]
    
    Answer --> Grade[AI Evaluates and Grades]
    Grade --> MoreQ{More Questions?}

    MoreQ -->|Yes| Answer
    
    %% Conclusion Path
    MoreQ -->|No| Review[Review Final Score and Mistakes]
    Review --> UpdateMastery[Update Mastery Statistics]
    
    UpdateMastery --> Finish